  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this observational study is to investigate the management and the
      complications associated wtih surgically treated peritonitis.

      Data will be analysed to answer pre-defined scientific projects and to improve management of
      these conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Anonymous data will be collected by study coordinators in a secured e-database. Cross audit
      will be performed to check data.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
